1111
01:33:20,678 --> 01:33:25,844
Mr. Oswalt, what kind of book
are you writing exactly?

1112
01:33:28,394 --> 01:33:32,558
I don't know. I'm not even
sure I have a book anymore.

1113
01:33:32,982 --> 01:33:34,472
